        <inbodydescription>
<para>Calculate the modulo of a number. The % operator in C++ is not a modulo operator, but a remainder operator. Therefore, when the dividend is negative, the result is also negative. This function calculates the modulo of a number in the correct way.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>a</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The dividend </para>
